Program: Discovery
Title: Designer Sperm
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrw6l
Last Broadcast Date: 11 April 1994
Report into the genetic alteration of sperm in laboratory animals: could it one day be used on humans too? Also, the battle to beat the antibiotic resistance bacteria - "superbugs": How photographic telescopes are still being used to good effect. Presented by Roland Pease.